The '''Sabloal Valea Dacilor Wind Farm''' is an under construction [[wind power]] project in [[Constanţa County]], [[Romania]]. It will consist of 49 individual [[wind turbine]]s<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.zf.ro/companii/energie/investitorii-nu-s-au-grabit-doar-4-din-proiectele-eoliene-pot-demara-3939328/|title=Investitorii nu s-au grabit: doar 4% din proiectele eoliene pot demara|date=2009-03-04|work=zf.ro|publisher=Ziarul Financiar|language=Romanian|accessdate=2009-03-04}}</ref> with a nominal output of around 3 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] which will deliver up to 147 MW of power, enough to power over 96,285 homes, with a capital investment required of approximately US$200 million.

